    background-color: #E8F5FD;

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">'Nowhere is out of bounds.' North Dorset Labour Party's sentiments exactly! <a href="/hashtag/JC4PM?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>JC4PM</b></a><a href="https://t.co/VWvDdYUuJD" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/963744888708722692" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/963744888708722692"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/963744888708722692</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Pat Osborne added,</p>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Its disgraceful that the richest 1% have 82% of the worlds wealth. We must end the rigged system that has enriched the few, at the expense of the many, here in the UK and around the world.<a href="https://t.co/F78HQsjb9Q" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-42745853" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/business-42745853"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">http://www.</span><span class="js-display-url">bbc.co.uk/news/business-</span><span class="invisible">42745853</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Pat Osborne Retweeted Simon Hoare MP</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">I went in today myself.
1) Part true. Yeovil, Yes. Some Poole postcodes. Not all.
2) 17 Jan for Blandford and remaining Poole postcodes. 
Not postponed. Just innaccurately communicated on Gov.UK. Absolute shambles of a rollout causing unnecessary worry. Please pause and rethink.<a href="https://t.co/nSLfjQtnNS" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/Simon4NDorset/status/933123827890081792" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/Simon4NDorset/status/933123827890081792"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/Simon4NDorset/</span><span class="invisible">status/933123827890081792</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Here are our pledges to pensioners and older people. Well ensure you have the security and dignity you deserve. RT <a href="https://t.co/u2pgplIkGA" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" data-pre-embedded="true" dir="ltr">pic.twitter.com/u2pgplIkGA</a></p>
</div>

    </div>

        <div class="PlayableMedia-externalUrlBlockContent">
          <div class="PlayableMedia-title">Our pledges to older people</div>
          <div class="PlayableMedia-description">Labour will keep the triple lock on pensions, protect Winter Fuel Allowance &amp; offer justice for the WASPI women. Well ensure you have the security and dignity you deserve. </div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">They're trying to stop you reading about Dementia Tax. That's Dementia Tax. Dementia Tax? Think about that for a minute. Dementia Tax.<a href="https://t.co/Svf3U1GKvD" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/independent/status/866569875027886080" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/independent/status/866569875027886080"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/independent/st</span><span class="invisible">atus/866569875027886080</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Gary Lineker added,</p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Jeremy Corbyn Retweeted Scottish Labour</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Congrats to Labour councillors elected in Scotland. Some results were disappointing but we will continue to fight for the Scottish people.<a href="https://t.co/pJNyArpip6" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/scottishlabour/status/860487021483225088" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/scottishlabour/status/860487021483225088"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/scottishlabour</span><span class="invisible">/status/860487021483225088</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Jeremy Corbyn added,</p>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Tories reduced to desperate lies. Concerning Chancellor cannot distinguish between current and capital expenditure<a href="https://t.co/E1yhWTuht3" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/premnsikka/status/859700690549125121" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/premnsikka/status/859700690549125121"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/premnsikka/sta</span><span class="invisible">tus/859700690549125121</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

        <div class="embed-include-parent-tweet">

      </div>
    </div>
  </form>
